# 💖 ⎯᪵⎯꯭̽🤍꯭᪳ ⃪𝗖𝘂꯭𝘁𝗶𝗲꯭ 𝗣𝗶𝗲꯭ ⃪🌸͎᪳᪳𝆺꯭𝅥⎯꯭̽⎯꯭ : Aapki Pyari Self-Learning Telegram Bot! 💖

Namaste, mere pyaare dosto! 👋 Main hoon ⎯᪵⎯꯭̽🤍꯭᪳ ⃪𝗖𝘂꯭𝘁𝗶𝗲꯭ 𝗣𝗶𝗲꯭ ⃪🌸͎᪳᪳𝆺꯭𝅥⎯꯭̽⎯꯭, aapki apni smart aur cute self-learning Telegram bot! Main aapki baaton se seekhti hoon, aapke groups mein masti karti hoon, aur aapki har command par khadi utarti hoon. Meri har baat mein thodi si masti aur bahot saara pyaar hoga! 🥰

**Mera Ek Chota Sa Demo Dekho Yahan:** 👉 [@askiangelbot](https://t.me/askiangelbot)

Is README file mein main aapko apne baare mein saari jaankari dungi. Chalo, shuru karte hain! 😉

## ✨ Mere Features (Dekho, kitni pyaari hain!):

* **Self-Learning Superpower!** 🧠
    * Main groups mein hone wali conversations se seekhti hoon aur unhe yaad rakhti hoon. Jaise jaise aap baatein karte ho, main aur bhi smart hoti jaungi! Meri har baat mein naya rang hoga! 🎨
    * Contextual replies dene mein expert hoon. Agar aap kisi message ka reply karte ho, toh main uske hisaab se hi cute sa jawaab dungi.
* **Masti Bhari Commands!** 💖
    * Meri saari commands ko maine aise banaya hai ki aapko maza aaye.
    * `start`, `help`, `stats`, `myid`, `chatid` jaise basic commands se lekar, admin commands tak, sab kuch mere paas hai.
* **Admin Commands (Sirf mere Malik ke liye, shhh!)** 👑
    * `broadcast`, `resetdata`, `deletemessage`, `ban`, `unban`, `kick`, `pin`, `unpin` jaise powerful tools mere Malik ke liye.
    * Custom welcome messages set karne ki suvidha bhi hai: `setwelcome`, `getwelcome`, `clearwelcome`.
* **Clone My Cuteness (Premium)!** 👯‍♀️
    * Haan, aap mere jaisa apna khud ka pyaara sa bot bhi bana sakte ho! Bas chota sa payment karo, aur main aapko guidance dungi.
    * Isme bot token verification aur custom update channel set karne ki suvidha bhi hai.

## 🚀 Kaise Deploy Karein Meri Pyari Bot Ko? (Koyeb par!)

Mujhe online lane ke liye aap Koyeb ka use kar sakte ho. Yeh ekdum easy aur free hai (basic usage ke liye)!

### 📝 Step-by-Step Deployment Guide:

1.  **GitHub Repository Fork Karein:**
    * Sabse pehle, is repository ko fork kar lo. Isse iska ek copy aapke GitHub account mein ban jayega, jise aap apni marzi se modify kar sakte ho.
    * **Link to Fork:** [Your GitHub Repo Link Here] - *Replace with your actual GitHub repo link*
2.  **Koyeb Account Banayein:**
    * Agar aapka Koyeb par account nahi hai, toh [www.koyeb.com](https://www.koyeb.com) par jaakar sign up kar lo.
3.  **Naya Service Banayein:**
    * Koyeb dashboard par `Create Service` par click karein.
    * `Deploy from Git` option ko chunein.
    * Apne forked GitHub repository ko select karein.
    * Branch `main` (ya jo bhi aap use kar rahe ho) select karein.
4.  **Build Settings:**
    * **Builder:** `Docker` select karein.
    * **Environment:** `Python`
    * **Build Command:** `pip install -r requirements.txt` (Yeh meri zaroorat ki saari libraries install kar dega)
    * **Run Command:** `python main.py` (Yeh meri main file ko chalayega)
5.  **Environment Variables Set Karein (Bahut Zaroori Hai!):**
    * `Add Environment Variable` par click karein aur niche diye gaye variables ko fill karein.
    * **Yeh secrets hain, inhe kisi ke saath share mat karna!** 🤫

    | Variable Name              | Value Description                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
    | :------------------------- | :------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
    | `BOT_TOKEN`                | Apne bot ka token jo aapko @BotFather se milega. (Example: `1234567890:AAH_XYZABC...`)                                                                                                                                   |
    | `API_ID`                   | Apni Telegram API ID jo aap [my.telegram.org](https://my.telegram.org) se generate karoge. (Example: `1234567`)                                                                                                                                     |
    | `API_HASH`                 | Apni Telegram API Hash jo aap [my.telegram.org](https://my.telegram.org) se generate karoge. (Example: `abcd1234efgh5678ijkl9012mnop3456`)                                                                                                        |
    | `OWNER_ID`                 | Aapki (bot owner ki) Telegram User ID. Yeh integer mein hoti hai. (Example: `1234567890`) - *Important for admin commands!* |
    | `MONGO_DB_URI`             | MongoDB Atlas connection string. Yeh mere learning data (messages) ko store karne ke liye use hogi. Aapko Atlas se `SRV` link copy karna hoga. (Example: `mongodb+srv://user:pass@cluster.mongodb.net/database?retryWrites=true&w=majority`) |
    | `PORT`                     | `8000` (Koyeb ke liye default port)                                                                                                                                                                                       |

    * **Note:** Code mein maine do additional MongoDB URIs hardcoded ki hain (`CLONE_AND_STATE_MONGO_DB_URI` aur `COMMANDS_AND_BUTTONS_MONGO_DB_URI`). Agar aap chahte hain ki yeh bhi Environment Variables se aayein, toh aapko code mein badlaav karna hoga. Filhaal, yeh hardcoded URIs kaam karengi, lekin security ke liye variables behtar hain.

6.  **Deploy Karein!**
    * Saari settings karne ke baad, `Deploy` button par click karein.
    * Koyeb aapki bot ko build aur deploy karna shuru kar dega. Ismein thoda time lag sakta hai.
    * Jab status `Healthy` ho jaye, toh samajh lo main live aa gayi hoon! 🎉

## 🛠️ Troubleshooting (Agar Kuch Gadbad Ho Jaye!)

Agar main theek se kaam nahi kar rahi hoon, toh ghabrao mat! Yahan kuch tips hain:

1.  **Koyeb Logs Check Karein:**
    * Koyeb dashboard par apne deployed service ke `Logs` tab mein jao. Yahan saari errors aur warnings dikhengi. Yeh sabse pehla step hai! Agar koi error mile, toh mere support group mein screenshot share karna.
2.  **Environment Variables Dubara Check Karein:**
    * Ek bhi galat character ya extra space aapki bot ko band kar sakta hai. `BOT_TOKEN`, `API_ID`, `API_HASH`, `OWNER_ID`, aur `MONGO_DB_URI` ko dhyan se check karein.
3.  **MongoDB Connection:**
    * Ensure ki tumhari MongoDB URI (connection string) sahi hai aur IP whitelisting kiya hua hai (agar required ho) taaki Koyeb usse connect kar sake. `0.0.0.0/0` ko whitelist karna sabse easy hai.
4.  **BotFather par Commands Set Karein:**
    * Agar meri commands Telegram ke type bar mein nahi dikh rahi hain, toh @BotFather par jao, `Edit Bot` -> `Edit Commands` par click karo, aur niche diya gaya text paste kar do:

    ```
    start - Bot ko shuru kare
    stats - Bot ke statistics dekhe
    help - Bot ke commands aur suvidhaen dekhe
    myid - Apni user ID dekhe
    chatid - Current chat ki ID dekhe
    clonebot - Apna khud ka bot deploy karein (Premium)
    broadcast - Sabhi chats par message bhejein (Owner Only)
    resetdata - Database se data delete karein (Owner Only)
    deletemessage - Specific message ko database se hatayein (Owner Only)
    ban - User ko group se ban karein (Owner Only)
    unban - User ko group se unban karein (Owner Only)
    kick - User ko group se kick karein (Owner Only)
    pin - Message ko group mein pin karein (Owner Only)
    unpin - Sabhi pinned messages ko unpin karein (Owner Only)
    setwelcome - Group ke liye custom welcome message set karein (Owner Only)
    getwelcome - Group ka set kiya hua welcome message dekhe (Owner Only)
    clearwelcome - Group ka custom welcome message hatayein (Owner Only)
    ```
5.  **Bot Permissions (Groups mein):**
    * Agar admin commands (like `ban`, `pin`) group mein kaam nahi kar rahi hain, toh ensure karein ki aapne mujhe group mein `Add Admins` section se zaroori permissions di hain (e.g., `Ban Members`, `Pin Messages`).

